modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod adds a Milling Machine to craft “Parts” and recipes for all of the new parts in Alpha 18.

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/11141-del-stryker-a17-modlet-collection/).
